msgid "Developing a pipeline"
msgstr "开发流水线"

msgid ""
"Klein for Ray builds one directed dataflow graph and chooses batch or "
"streaming execution from its sources. Create sources directly from :mod:`ray."
"klein`, add transforms, attach at least one sink, and execute the current "
"graph."
msgstr "Klein for Ray 构建一张有向数据流图，并根据其数据源选择批处理或流处理执行。从 :mod:`ray.klein` 直接创建数据源，添加转换，连接至少一个 Sink，然后执行当前图。"

msgid "Execution modes"
msgstr "执行模式"

msgid ""
"Bounded Ray Data sources such as CSV, Parquet, JSON, and ``from_items`` use "
"batch execution. Long-running sources such as Kafka and user-defined "
"``SourceFunction`` implementations use streaming execution. Applications can "
"override automatic detection with ``ExecutionOptions.MODE``."
msgstr "CSV、Parquet、JSON 和 ``from_items`` 等有限 Ray Data 数据源使用批处理执行。Kafka 和用户定义的 ``SourceFunction`` 实现等长期运行的数据源使用流处理执行。应用可以通过 ``ExecutionOptions.MODE`` 覆盖自动检测结果。"

msgid "Transform functions"
msgstr "转换函数"

msgid ""
"``map``, ``flat_map``, and ``filter`` operate on record dictionaries. "
"``map_batches`` accepts a dictionary of columns and is preferred for "
"vectorized workloads such as model inference. A callable class can request a "
"``runtime_context`` constructor argument to inspect its task index or "
"register metrics."
msgstr "``map``、``flat_map`` 和 ``filter`` 操作记录字典。``map_batches`` 接收列字典，更适合模型推理等向量化工作负载。可调用类可以声明 ``runtime_context`` 构造参数，以查看任务索引或注册指标。"

msgid "Source and sink lifecycle"
msgstr "Source 和 Sink 生命周期"

msgid ""
"Pass ``SourceFunction`` and ``SinkFunction`` implementations as classes, "
"along with constructor arguments, so every physical subtask owns one "
"independent instance. Passing a pre-created lifecycle object is rejected "
"because it can share mutable state or network connections across subtasks."
msgstr "请以类以及构造参数的形式传入 ``SourceFunction`` 和 ``SinkFunction`` 实现，使每个物理子任务拥有一个独立实例。预先创建的生命周期对象会被拒绝，因为它可能在多个子任务之间共享可变状态或网络连接。"

msgid ""
"For a streaming source, ``cancel()`` is the cooperative stop signal for the "
"running loop. Keep resource release in ``close()``; the runtime invokes it "
"once after the loop exits. Sink ``flush()`` publishes buffered writes at "
"aligned barriers, while ``close()`` performs final resource cleanup."
msgstr "对于流处理 Source，``cancel()`` 是运行循环的协作式停止信号。资源释放应放在 ``close()`` 中；循环退出后，运行时会调用它一次。Sink 的 ``flush()`` 会在对齐屏障处发布缓冲写入，而 ``close()`` 负责最终的资源清理。"

msgid "Resources and partitioning"
msgstr "资源与分区"

msgid ""
"Sources, transforms, and sinks accept ``num_cpus``, ``num_gpus``, and "
"``concurrency``. Streaming graphs also support ``round_robin``, ``rescale``, "
"``adaptive_shuffle``, and ``partition_by``. Keep resource requests explicit "
"for production graphs and validate them with ``ray.klein.explain`` before "
"deployment."
msgstr "Source、转换和 Sink 接受 ``num_cpus``、``num_gpus`` 和 ``concurrency``。流处理图还支持 ``round_robin``、``rescale``、``adaptive_shuffle`` 和 ``partition_by``。生产图应明确指定资源请求，并在部署前使用 ``ray.klein.explain`` 进行验证。"

msgid "Connectors"
msgstr "连接器"

msgid ""
"The core distribution supports Ray Data connectors, collections, Kafka, "
"filesystems, Redis, console output, and custom sources or sinks. Ray Serve "
"is an optional execution integration. The dedicated :doc:`connector catalog "
"<connectors/index>` provides a capability matrix and a separate page for "
"every connector, including options, defaults, schemas, and delivery "
"guarantees."
msgstr "核心发行版支持 Ray Data 连接器、集合、Kafka、文件系统、Redis、控制台输出以及自定义 Source 或 Sink。Ray Serve 是可选的执行集成。专门的 :doc:`连接器目录 <connectors/index>` 提供能力矩阵，并为每种连接器提供独立页面，其中包括选项、默认值、模式和交付保证。"

msgid ""
"Service discovery and organization-specific storage clients are "
"intentionally outside the core package. Optional connectors should be "
"separate distributions that depend on ``ray-klein`` and may expose a Table "
"factory through the ``ray.klein.table_factories`` entry-point group."
msgstr "服务发现和组织专用的存储客户端有意不包含在核心包中。可选连接器应作为依赖 ``ray-klein`` 的独立发行版，并可通过 ``ray.klein.table_factories`` 入口点组公开 Table 工厂。"

msgid ""
"See :ref:`klein-context-api`, :ref:`data-stream-api`, and :ref:"
"`configuration-options-api` for the generated API reference."
msgstr "生成的 API 参考请参阅 :ref:`klein-context-api`、:ref:`data-stream-api` 和 :ref:`configuration-options-api`。"
